    <h2>Can you print in any other size other than a full size violin? </h2>
    <p>It is our goal to release models of the hovalin for all standard violin sizes. We currently have released 4/4. But next up is 1/2, followed by 1/4, and 3/4.


    <h2>Is the hovalin louder than standard violins?</h2>
    <p>No. Well, at least not yet. Following in the footsteps of other luthiers, our goal is to iterate on the violin's design to constantly increase acoustic output and improve playability.</p>
    <p>On the other hand, having a quieter instrument, with equal playability, has its benefits as an educational tool.</p>


